hotel_0.name: The Ritz-Carlton New York, NoMad
hotel_0.hotel_description: Located in New York, a 7-minute walk from Flatiron Building, The Ritz-Carlton New York, NoMad has accommodations with a fitness center, private parking, a garden and a bar. The property is close to several well-known attractions, a 7-minute walk from Macy's, 0.7 miles from Bryant Park and a 19-minute walk from Grand Central Station. The hotel has a sauna and a kids' club. An à la carte breakfast is available every morning at the hotel. At The Ritz-Carlton New York, NoMad you'll find a restaurant serving American, Mediterranean and Spanish cuisine. Vegetarian, vegan and dairy-free options can also be requested. Guests at the accommodation will be able to enjoy activities in and around New York, like cycling. Speaking German, English, Spanish and French, staff at the reception can help you plan your stay. Popular points of interest near The Ritz-Carlton New York, NoMad include Empire State Building, Madison Square Garden and Penn Station. The nearest airport is LaGuardia Airport, 7.5 miles from the hotel.

hotel_0.hotel_description: Modern Studio Less Than 13 Mi to Saratoga Racetrack! is located in Ballston Spa, 12 miles from Petrified Sea Gardens, 13 miles from National Museum of Racing and Hall of Fame, as well as 13 miles from Saratoga Golf Club. hotel_0.name: The Idlewyld Inn and Spa
hotel_0.hotel_description: Offering on-site dining facilities, this 19th-century inn is just just over 1 mile from the center of London, Ontario. A flat-screen TV is provided in each guest room. Styled in Victorian décor, each guest room at The Idlewyld Inn and Spa is furnished with a private bathroom and sitting area. A spa tub is featured in select rooms. Showcasing local ingredients, The Idlewyld Inn and Spa's on-site restaurant offers breakfast, lunch and dinner options. A varied wine selection is also available. In season, guests can dine on the terrace. Free Wi-Fi and parking are also accessible to guests staying at this London, Ontario inn. The Grand Theatre and the Budweiser Gardens are about a 5-minute drive from this inn. Fanshawe Pioneer Village is about a 20-minute drive away.
